dct_title_s: Geological map of New Jersey, from original surveys, 1889
dct_description_sm: Includes 2 cross sections. Historic Maps copy 1 is mounted on pasteboard. Historic Maps copy 2 is dissected in 16 pieces and mounted on cloth. "Atlas sheet no. 20." Historic Maps copy 2 has label on verso: Atlas of New Jersey. Map sheet no. 20. [In ms.]: Whole state.
